After going through the learning activities, and installing the five databases from the book's website, solve 
the following exercises from the "Problems for you to solve" section of chapter 4:

__________________________________________________________
School Schedule Database #1 - 
Show me a complete list of all the subjects we offer

SELECT DISTINCT SubjectName AS [Subjects WE Offer]
FROM Subjects
ORDER BY SubjectName ASC


//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
__________________________________________________________
School Schedule Database #2 - 
What kinds of titles are associated with our faculty?

SELECT DISTINCT Title AS [Titles]
FROM Faculty
ORDER BY Titles
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
__________________________________________________________
Bowling League Database #1 - 
List all of the teams in alphabetical order

SELECT Distinct TeamName AS 'Teams by Alphabet'
FROM Teams
ORDER BY Team ASC
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
__________________________________________________________
